race.comment: BULLFIGHTER (3) resumes from a spell of 13 months. Has filled a minor placing at both first-up runs. Opened last prep with a third over 1000m at Canberra. Expected to run well. SCION (4) bounced back to form with a second place run at this track after a less than encouraging eighth at Gold Coast Poly two back. Further improvement can see him in the finish. TAYLOR'S RAGE (0) looks an improver second up back to this sort of level. ATHOL MAC (1) was in the money two starts back at Bell but couldn't back it up last time when ninth, beaten 18 lengths, at Kilcoy over 1200m. Suitably placed so anticipating a big run this time.
